<span id="freeTextContainer4961704928813354851">I had been planning to read this one for ages. Finally got the time to do it. <br/>I was pleasantly surprised. Great language and great story. Full of weird and wonderful characters and incidents, and a mixture of strange humour and sadness. Loved it!</span>

